domosaics.model.workspace
Class WorkspaceElement

java.lang.Object
  domosaics.model.workspace.WorkspaceElement
Direct Known Subclasses:
CategoryElement, ProjectElement, ViewElement, Workspace
public abstract class WorkspaceElement
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract WorkspaceElement defines the basic methods which apply to all kinds of workspace elements. For instance the methods used by the TreeModel.

In general there exist 4 types of workspace elements, the workspace itself, projects, view categories and views.

Author:
Andreas Held
